text: Didier Willefert (born 2 August 1964) is a French equestrian. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Marseille
